00:08:33.620 --> 00:08:35.940
And what is the area of that strip?

00:08:35.940 --> 00:08:39.240
It is f(x), that's the height of the rectangle

00:08:40.160 --> 00:08:42.160
multiplied by

00:08:42.740 --> 00:08:44.340
this little base.

